column1: ## in Stocker et al.
## Provided are summary statistics based on a set of 1000 individual Monte Carlo
## simulations. Values are given at a decadal time step and are representative of
## annual values within the decade starting in 'year'-5 and ending in 'year'+4.
## This data is used to create Fig. S1 in Stocker et al.
## are provided here due to autogenic effects affecting younger peat.
## Citation: Stocker et al.: Holocene peatland and ice core data constraints on
## the timing and magnitude of CO2 emissions from past land use
## This data is made available under the GNU General Public License v3.0
## Columns description:
## 1.  age          year before present (1950 CE)
## 2.  year         year CE
## 3.  mean         mean over 1000 MC simulations (PgC yr-1)
## 4.  median       median of 1000 MC simulations (PgC yr-1)
## 5.  sd           standard deviation of 1000 MC simulations (PgC yr-1)
## 6.  q10          10%-quantile of 1000 MC simulations (PgC yr-1)
## 7.  q90          90%-quantile of 1000 MC simulations (PgC yr-1)
